372
00:20:35,210 --> 00:20:37,210
A svedl mě.

373
00:20:38,930 --> 00:20:40,400
George. Mobil.

374
00:20:41,250 --> 00:20:42,810
Oh ne... srdce mi bije tak rychle!

375
00:20:43,140 --> 00:20:44,250
